caption.p: The levels of 5-HT ( A), NM ( B), GLN ( C), and GABA ( D), and excitatory/inhibitory ratio ( E) in brain samples of zebrafish exposed to GM-90432, PTZ, or PTZ following pretreatment with GM-90432. Values represent means Â± standard error of the mean (SEM) of 12 samples. Significance between control and exposure groups is indicated by * p < 0.05, ** p < 0.01, and *** p < 0.001.
